b'Jonathan, Admin Assistant and ASL Student.
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\x9cWhen I got the call from Progressive, I was jumping around screaming!\xe2\x80\x9d Jonathan recalls the day he got hired and how excited he was to start in our House Counsel office in #NewJersey. Turns out, legal administration wasn\xe2\x80\x99t all he signed-up to learn. As Jonathan settled into his position, he found out that two of his coworkers were deaf. So right away, he started learning sign language in order to be a better teammate. Every day he picked up a few more signs. \xe2\x80\x9cI\xe2\x80\x99ve already learned so much more than I ever thought and it\xe2\x80\x99s only been sixteen months!\xe2\x80\x9d :clapping_hands::clapping_hands::clapping_hands: Jonathan says learning a whole new language has not only helped him personally, but professionally, \xe2\x80\x9cI know my coworkers appreciate it but it\xe2\x80\x99s truly been an invaluable learning experience for me, too.\xe2\x80\x9d

b'Eliani, Photo Estimator and Proud Citizen.
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
Born in the Dominican Republic, Eliani shifted between the U.S. and D.R. before settling in Cleveland. And when she started at Progressive two years ago, she felt right at home. In fact, when it came to acing her American citizenship exam, her co-workers were her greatest cheerleaders. \xe2\x80\x9cMy family at Progressive is so tight and supportive. I never expected it to be so good here.\xe2\x80\x9d Now, as part of Progressive\xe2\x80\x99s photo estimation group, Eliani helps customers decide whether their damaged vehicles should be repaired or replaced. She wants to be a role model for her son, Liam, by teaching him to strive for excellence. \xe2\x80\x9cProgressive sets the bar high and I\xe2\x80\x99m proud to be a part of that.\xe2\x80\x9d 

#PeopleofProgressive #PGREmployee #LifeatProgressive #RethinkProgressive #HispanicHeritageMonth #Claims #Immigrant #ThisisCLE'

b'Michael, IT Systems Analyst and Former Barista. 
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
Many Progressive employees might remember Michael from behind the coffee bar, because it was only a couple years ago that he was serving up lattes at the Campus 2 caf\xc3\xa9. Turns out, whipping up delicious drinks isn\xe2\x80\x99t the only skill Michael brings to the table. :slightly_smiling_face: In fact, he mentioned to a caf\xc3\xa9 customer one day that he was getting a degree in Information Technology. She said they were hiring summer interns and encouraged Michael to apply. He collected great advice from his customers on how to nail his S.T.A.R. interview and now, he\xe2\x80\x99s a full-time employee with Progressive. These days, Michael is building a whole new data center with project teams; validating applications and servers and meeting with subject matter experts from all different business areas. \xe2\x80\x9cI\xe2\x80\x99ve always loved talking to people. This time, it really paid off.\xe2\x80\x9d #PeopleofProgressive #PGREmployee #LifeatProgressive #RethinkProgressive #IT #Systems #Analyst'

b'Benjamin, IT Quality Assurance Analyst and Guitar Maker.
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
As an IT Quality Assurance Analyst, it\xe2\x80\x99s no surprise that Ben has high standards. What started with reading a book from his step-dad, turned into a passion for lutherie - the art of making wooden, stringed musical instruments. Always driven to learn more, Ben used books and online research to turn his interest into a fulfilling hobby. \xe2\x80\x9cI love improving on every instrument. Starting and finishing each guitar feels better than actually playing it.\xe2\x80\x9d To date, Ben has made 10 custom electric guitars - constructing, sanding, and oiling each one by hand, \xe2\x80\x9cFor me, quality is always key.\xe2\x80\x9d #PeopleofProgressive #LifeatProgressive #RethinkProgressive #IT #Quality #Analyst #Guitar #Maker #Lutherie'

b'Kerry, Underwriting Resolution Consultant and licensed skydiver.
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
Once Kerry got to the ground after her first skydive, she couldn\xe2\x80\x99t wait to go back up! Whenever she needs a confidence boost - like the day she interviewed at Progressive - she reminds herself, \xe2\x80\x9cKerry, you jump out of planes, you can do anything!\xe2\x80\x9d To date, she\xe2\x80\x99s up to 130 jumps and counting. \xe2\x80\x9cThe airplane door opens and the sound of wind comes rushing in, then you step foot out of the door, and it\xe2\x80\x99s absolute bliss. It\xe2\x80\x99s like meditation.\xe2\x80\x9d Kerry used to be hesitant to tell people her hobby since she does work in risk mitigation after all, but when she told her Progressive crew, \xe2\x80\x9csome of them actually wanted in!\xe2\x80\x9d #PeopleofProgressive #LifeatProgressive #RethinkProgressive #Underwriter #Skydive #Thrillseeker'

b'Stacy, IT Apps Programmer and Scrum Master
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
A bit of an introvert, Stacy never thought that one day she\xe2\x80\x99d be leading a team of programmers in a Scrum master role. \xe2\x80\x9cThe Scrum framework helps us do twice the work in half the time.\xe2\x80\x9d Part of her unique strategy is walking away from the work for some silly play. \xe2\x80\x9cI brought in games to help us relax and get more comfortable with one another. As a result we\xe2\x80\x99ve been more adaptive, self-organized, and efficient.\xe2\x80\x9d Stacy feels wholly committed to the team and sets new goals every week. \xe2\x80\x9cIt\xe2\x80\x99s been so rewarding to work through challenges this way and come out stronger - to me, that\xe2\x80\x99s the true culture of Progressive.\xe2\x80\x9d #IT #Apps #Programmer #Scrum'

b'Anand, IT Apps Programmer/Scrum Master and Youth Leader.
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
Having grown up in scouting programs, Anand learned early on about the rewards of hard work. Maybe it was his dedication back then that set him up for his role developing the Progressive Policy Servicing app. A member of AANET, our Asian American Employee Resource Group, Anand is applying the same diversity and inclusion principles to his kids who are now enrolled in the same youth programs. He\xe2\x80\x99s taught them about different faiths, shared cuisines from different cultures, as well as demonstrated basic outdoor skills. \xe2\x80\x9cI am reliving my childhood through my own kids now and I believe I\xe2\x80\x99m benefitting as much as they are.\xe2\x80\x9d #IT #Apps #Programmer #Scrum #Scouting #PeopleofProgressive'

b'Beth, Digital Designer and therapy horse trainer.
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
Beth got her start at Progressive back in 1984 when there were no computers and vacation time was tracked on paper. She began in payroll, eventually moving to HR, then IT and now she\xe2\x80\x99s a digital designer for our Claims Training team. \xe2\x80\x9cProgressive has always challenged me to keep growing and learning - it keeps me very interested in what I do.\xe2\x80\x9d In 2005, Beth joined a local therapeutic riding center when her daughter went off to college and it became a real passion of hers to work with the therapy horses and students. \xe2\x80\x9cWorking with horses is now a big part of who I am and I feel very lucky to be supported by my family at home and my family at work.\xe2\x80\x9d #PeopleofProgressive #LifeatProgressive #RethinkProgressive #DigitalDesigner #Horse #Trainer #Therapy'

b'Daniel, CRM Supervisor and Air Force veteran.
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
\xe2\x80\xa2
When Daniel started at Progressive six years ago, he knew it was a place that would nurture his career. He didn\xe2\x80\x99t expect it would be a place to nurture his passions, too. He grew from a new member of the sales team to a supervisor in just three years. \xe2\x80\x9cSo many people bring themselves to work here that I felt comfortable in the space from day one.\xe2\x80\x9d A veteran of the Air Force, Daniel decided to start a speaker series within our military network called \xe2\x80\x9cMILNET Means\xe2\x80\x9d which invites veteran speakers to share how their experiences mirror their careers at Progressive. \xe2\x80\x9cI\xe2\x80\x99ve found the same camaraderie at Progressive as I had in the military. Our people truly care about making an impact and we believe in what we do every day.\xe2\x80\x9d #PeopleOfProgressive #LifeAtProgressive #RethinkProgressive #AirForce #Military #Veteran #CRM'
